Changes made by Pranav Agrawal (2025):
- Updated regular expressions for improved user-agent parsing.
- Added an automation script to update user-agent regexes on demand.
- Implemented CLI tool for easy updating of regexes.
- Fixed bug where user-agent patterns were not properly matching newer browser versions.
